step_data.thought: The user is currently on the 'Default Addresses' section of the 'Manage Addresses' page. The next step is to allow the user to choose whether to change their default billing or shipping address, or to add a new address. Since the previous action was to click on 'Default Addresses', the user is already on the correct section. Now, the user can choose to change their default billing or shipping address or add a new one.
